{"type": "article", "id": 19155, "title": "烧烤酱包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-16T07:32:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071042133ZtMVRFovA54d9Gw.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是新西兰的平面设计工作室 Spasm Studio 为一家烧烤店 Alderson’s 设计的包装，使用了 Morepork（莫勒波克蛙嘴夜鹰）的名字和图案，在深蓝色的背景上画出黄色眼睛和海报字体，有强烈的对比和神秘感。Morepork 是在澳大利亚和东南亚一带活动的夜间动物，图案近似一只猫头鹰，很有故事，营造出夜晚吃烧烤的气氛。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145805YG2NXdJ9ULjRcBZk.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145806ZIqBreC0pfl7FwLM.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145807o06UT5WmM3LehQcq.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261458072yJSeXvHDuV5TNdL.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}